Class LoadDict

java.lang.Object
  dicomreader.LoadDict

public class LoadDict
extends java.lang.Object

The LoadDict class opens the Dicom tags dictionary.
It will be needed by the DicomReader class operations on Dicom tags.

Version:
1.3
Author:
Salvatore La Bua < slabua (at) gmail.com >
